    - Bump debhelper B-D to >= 8.1, for build-{arch,indep} support.
  * Bump debhelper compat level to 8.
  * Bump machine readable copyright format to 1.0.
  * Re-licence packaging under Expat.
  * Switch debian/watch URL to https.
